698
00:40:54,720 --> 00:40:55,990
Ada apa ini?

699
00:40:56,050 --> 00:40:57,320
Apa ini?

700
00:41:00,490 --> 00:41:01,320
Ada apa?

701
00:41:01,390 --> 00:41:03,060
- Coba tebak?
- Apa?

702
00:41:03,130 --> 00:41:06,230
Meja Direktur Akina
yang luar biasa dan menawan

703
00:41:06,300 --> 00:41:09,170
dan Pangeran Kaoru kita yang karismatik,

704
00:41:09,230 --> 00:41:14,540
